ubtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02292">Schnitzler an Brandes, 2. 8. 1918</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02290">Schnitzler an Adam, 24. 7. 1918</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02293">Schnitzler an Adam, 6. 8. 1918</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
